THIRD-PARTY SERVICES AND DEPENDENCIES
================================================================================

Pillar uses the following third-party services and open-source components:

EXTERNAL API SERVICES (Used via Network APIs)
----------------------------------------------
These services are accessed over the network and do not affect the licensing
of this project:

* FireCrawl API (https://firecrawl.dev)
  - Used for web crawling and content extraction
  - Server: AGPL-3.0 (https://github.com/mendableai/firecrawl)
  - Python SDK (firecrawl-py): MIT License
  - We use only the API client, not the server code

* OpenAI API (https://openai.com)
  - Used for large language model services
  - Python SDK: Apache-2.0 / MIT License

* Anthropic API (https://anthropic.com)
  - Used for Claude AI services
  - Python SDK: MIT License

